creator: Mobile App @ Cradlewise
descriptionHtml:
Download the Cradlewise App

The Cradlewise app is designed so that you spend quality time with your baby. The features that aid parents are :

Remote Control: You can set the duration and intensity of rocking through our app. The cradle has a nap or snooze mode which makes it responsive to the baby’s early wake-up signals - automagically rocking your baby back to sleep along with soothing music.

Monitoring: A live video stream on your phone allows you to see your baby remotely - either from a different room or while you are at work. You can choose the background audio monitoring mode for the time when you need to be handsfree.


Safety Alerts: Guaranteed peace of mind during day or night! The app notifies you when the baby needs you. Get alerts when the baby rolls over, a blanket covers the baby’s face or if baby is trying to sit up in the cradle.

Music: You can play music from our curated playlist or upload your own music through the Cradlewise app.

Sleep Analytics: Track your baby’s sleep and understand your baby’s sleep better. Our weekly sleep report gives you a summary of how well and how long your baby slept.

Sleep Tips: Get personalized sleep tips that help your baby sleep better and guide you through your parenting process.

descriptionHtml:

APP FEATURES

BUILT-IN BABY MONITOR. PEACE OF MIND FOR YOU.

NIGHT VISION: See your baby without turning on the lights and disturbing your little one.

creator: Mobile App @ Cradlewise
descriptionHtml:
WORLD'S FIRST SELF LEARNING CRIB. It spots early signs of wake-up, learns sleep patterns and automatically soothes your baby to sleep, if needed.

===========

IT'S A BASSINET AND A CRIB - FROM BIRTH TO 24 MONTHS :
Cradlewise provides uninterrupted quality sleep to babies and saves parents an average of 2 hours a day. It combines the functionality of a bassinet, crib, baby monitor and sound machine – all into one product.

GETS THE BABY TO SLEEP :
When it’s time to sleep, simply place your baby in the crib. The crib automatically detects the baby’s wakefulness and soothes them to sleep with its bounce and sound.

GUARDS SLEEP :
Just-in-time soothing is key to safeguarding baby sleep. The crib spots sleep disturbances and soothes the baby back to sleep.

===========

APP FEATURES

BUILT-IN BABY MONITOR. PEACE OF MIND FOR YOU.

NIGHT VISION: See your baby without turning on the lights and disturbing your little one.

NOTIFICATIONS: Get notified when your baby wakes up, falls asleep, starts crying etc.

LIVE VIDEO: Watch your baby live through your smartphone app from anywhere, anytime.

BACKGROUND AUDIO: Take a break or catch up on other work while listening to your baby in the background.

ROOM TEMPERATURE: The Cradlewise app has a room temperature monitoring feature that lets you quickly check your baby’s room temperature from the home screen, making it easier to to check anytime, anywhere.

ADD CAREGIVERS: We know that new parents already have their hands full. And since it takes a village to raise a child, our caregiver functionality provides you with just that - a virtual village. Add a caregiver and control the level of access.

DARK MODE: Dark mode reduces the brightness level on your phone, and it’s a game changer for minimizing light disruptions at night, especially when you want to check on them at 3am in the morning.


WATCH YOUR BABY’S SLEEP IMPROVE OVER TIME.

DAILY SNAPSHOT: Track your baby’s sleep patterns and stay on top of changes.

SLEEP TRACKING: Track your baby’s sleep data - understand patterns from historical logs to understand your baby’s sleep better.

QUICK TIPS: User guides and tips to help you best adjust your crib’s settings to improve your baby’s sleep.


CURATED SOOTHING MUSIC

BUILT-IN SOUND MACHINE: Curated white, pink and brown noise tracks to calm a fussy baby. Option to create your own soundtrack.

BABY SAFE VOLUME: Smart mode stops sound when the baby has fallen asleep. Sound volume is capped to 60dB to be safe for your baby.

STREAM MUSIC OVER SPOTIFY TO THE CRIB: This feature allows you to turn your cradle into a speaker by enabling you to pair your crib with the Spotify app. You can curate a Spotify playlist for your little one and can play your favorite pop songs, lullabies, nursery rhymes, soothing sounds, or whatever they’re into, from wherever you happen to be.
